description: Dishes From Around The World and Curbside Curries. Bringing you flavorful, healthy food that will wake up your taste buds. As seen on season 6 of The Great Food Truck Race, this truck is here to Spice It Up!Life wouldn't be the same without the many tastes, textures, ingredients and spices from around the world. In our dishes,we use spices as an artist uses a palette to tone and color the food.You pick the menu and we come to you, no mess to worry about. All the food is prepared and cooked on our truck. A new, fun and exciting concept for you and your guests.Come surprise yourself, we have a world of flavor.
name: Spice It Up
